AB  - This paper documents a preliminary empirical pattern surrounding token unlock events on Binance using 52 events from 2024 to early 2026. Short-window event studies reveal systematic negative abnormal returns concentrated in the 72-hour window following unlock, surviving market-beta adjustments and robustness checks.
