DA  - 2026/05/11
PB  - SSRN
M3  - SSRN Working Paper
SN  - 6688740
DO  - 10.2139/ssrn.6688740
UR  - https://ssrn.com/abstract=6688740
AB  - Examines the distribution-asymmetry structure of centralized-exchange airdrop campaigns, focusing on Binance's Megadrop program and the BNB Chain ecosystem. Decomposes realized economic outcomes across three stakeholder cohorts (BNB holders, project foundations, retail participants) and documents systematic BNB-holder gains, foundation losses, and a cross-domain decoupling pattern between BNB Chain on-chain activity and Megadrop token prices.
